Title: Terma (2)
Plot: While imprisoned in Russia and infected with the Black Cancer, Mulder learns that Krycek is working with the men responsible and everything has been a setup from the start, while Scully and Skinner are called to a suspicious Senate hearing where the only question is the whereabouts of Agent Mulder.
GuestStars: Jessica Schreier, Brent Stait, Malcolm Stewart, Campbell Lane, Robin Mossley, Brenda McDonald, Pamela MacDonald, Eileen Pedde, Stefan Arngrim, Jan Rube?, Fritz Weaver
